title: Native Instruments -Maschnie 2 Factory Library - PC and MAC
description:
I found this on my external hard drive after I tried setting up Maschine 2 on my new MAC and found I did not have the Factory Library.I just got this up and going with no hassles. PC installer and NI Activator included. Do not need the Activator for MAC, just drop the .iso on your MAC desktop and run the setup application. I suggest letting everything install to the default folders. 

Not my rip of course and thanks who ever did this and I am happy I found this. As is typical of me I will seed for a long a long time but not forever. I usually stop after a 2.000 ratio is attained and then it is up to others to show some interest in the material.

And remember, if you make money with the product... cool.  

Uranium Willy
